data.description: Step into the charm of this 1890 Cape Cod farmhouse, a 3-bed, 2-bath haven with timeless allure. The updated kitchen features an island, seamlessly blending modern convenience with rustic charm. Original hardwood floors grace every room, exuding warmth and character. A covered patio offers a delightful retreat overlooking the adjacent golf course, complemented by a spacious deck for outdoor entertaining. The basement provides extra space, while a dry-walled workshop caters to your hobbies. Kids will love the enchanting treehouse, completing the picturesque setting. This property is a perfect blend of history and modern living, surrounded by the scenic beauty of a golf course. Welcome to your dream home!
